Package:Weedmodels
Type: Package
Title: Classification of archaeobotanical data using linear discriminant analysis against modern models and plotting of the resultant discriminant scores
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Elizabeth Stroud
Maintainer: Elizabeth Stroud <elizabeth.stroud@arch.ox.ac.uk>
Description:  This package has functions which conduct linear discriminant analysis classification using one of three modern models (i.e. sets of discriminated modern arable fields) to classify archaeobotanical samples on the basis of relevant functional ecological attributes of weed species.
License: MIT
Depends:
  dplyr,
  MASS, 
  beeswarm
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
